    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Liferay SaaS or PaaS</h2>\n\n<p>Only administrators can begin the activation process for Liferay SaaS and Liferay PaaS. In order to verify if this process is complete or to accress your Liferay SaaS or Liferay PaaS environment:</p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>Navigate to support.liferay.com/projects or select Project in the top navigation</li>\n\t<li>Select your project if you are part of more than 1 project</li>\n\t<li>In the left-hand navigation, expand Activation</li>\n\t<li>Select either Liferay SaaS or Liferay PaaS</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2>Liferay Self-Hosted</h2>\n\n<p>Only administrators can generate activation keys for non developer environments. Other users can download activation keys which have already been generated or developer keys for Liferay DXP. To download activation keys:</p>\n\n<ol>\n\t<li>Navigate to support.liferay.com/projects or select Project in the top navigation</li>\n\t<li>Select your project if you are part of more than 1 project</li>\n\t<li>In the left-hand navigation, expand Activation</li>\n\t<li>Select DXP</li>\n\t<li>Locate your non developer activation key or under Developer Keys select your Liferay DXP version and download a key</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>For instructions on how to activate your Liferay DXP or Liferay Portal instance, please read the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/kb-article/deploying-activation-keys\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><u>deploying activation keys article.</u></a></p>"
      },
